  "detailed_description": "在这套交互视频课程《成为一名密码朋克》中，你会从玩乐里完成整个密码学的学习，从零开始，掌握密码学。​<br>​<br>密码学是现代生活的基石，也是当下火热的区块链和加密货币技术的前提。​<br>​<br>整个项目讲解了包括凯撒密码、维吉尼亚密码、Enigma 机器在内的古典密码，也深入到 DES、AES、RSA、Hash 算法等现代密码。​<br>​<br>现在，动起脑来，解密开始！​<br>​<br><strong>从零开始理解密码学核心概念​</strong><br>理解核心概念，不需任何基础。​<br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8346e5b22884e7454acf4bfc16ec370d.poster.avif?t=1633784823\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8346e5b22884e7454acf4bfc16ec370d.webm?t=1633784823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8346e5b22884e7454acf4bfc16ec370d.mp4?t=1633784823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>直观的三维可视化内容​</strong><br>三维可视化展示，轻松理解复杂原理。​<br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8e10c9216123a36f0d9ca3846256393a.poster.avif?t=1633784823\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8e10c9216123a36f0d9ca3846256393a.webm?t=1633784823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8e10c9216123a36f0d9ca3846256393a.mp4?t=1633784823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>在操作中理解复杂原理​</strong><br>角度、参数自由可调，在操作中理解复杂原理。​<br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8438f9b4d6ceb2db6a2cdb8e40923cb8.poster.avif?t=1633784823\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8438f9b4d6ceb2db6a2cdb8e40923cb8.webm?t=1633784823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/8438f9b4d6ceb2db6a2cdb8e40923cb8.mp4?t=1633784823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>充满挑战和惊喜的解谜任务​</strong><br>充满无限挑战的谜题，融合游戏、寻宝和情报等元素设计。​<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/6c55f67418ee22af676d85dad00d6100.poster.avif?t=1633784823\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/6c55f67418ee22af676d85dad00d6100.webm?t=1633784823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700250/extras/6c55f67418ee22af676d85dad00d6100.mp4?t=1633784823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
